{"tid":1641121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[FB戰線］大家一齊拯救下無知既阿叔阿嬸們！","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T09:37:05.000Z","uid":265917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"967408016187f45079bba93ab37a35b4a2e3f062","tid":1641121,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小妹發現facebook好少文宣流通 <br />\n我自己一個帶風向帶到好絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n要記住尼場革命吾係淨係屬於連登仔<br />\n<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地多數只會認同大眾都吹奏緊既野<br />\n<br />\n而藍屍page係fb大行其道<br />\n正所謂「識睇一定睇comment」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地要多啲係吾同post下面貼文宣 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n思想傳播好重要 <br />\n愚民之所以係愚民都係因為俾人洗得腦多 佢地唔知每件事既真相同事實<br />\n所以我地都要令文宣成為洗腦工具<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一張簡單既文宣唔多唔少可以影響到啲中佬既諗法<br />\n<br />\n咁先可以爭取到多啲老一輩既支持架!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該大家唔好淨係focus係twitter戰線 <br />\nFB戰線一樣咁撚重要</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">👇🏻啲阿叔阿嬸最中意睇尼啲地區谷既野 同我入曬去!!!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8nDfqj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8nDfqj.png&h=a6208431&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2345ee9ed3f9a458d65f38cdbe3d7dbc221d64c3","tid":1641121,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb34091b1c3047cf70d1c3ac98539360e2db69bd","tid":1641121,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"小妹帶風向帶到